    "gp_section_608890156979913271": {
      "settings": {
        "checksum": "ca2b11e320e66568fa5d7d8ee9abe2e8dcd8817397d727f2b907ee34a2620121_1_1_1_0__1",
        "gg81WwevIKk_childItem_0": "<p>Natural-looking tan</p>",
        "gg81WwevIKk_childItem_1": "<p>Lasts 3–4 days</p>",
        "gg81WwevIKk_childItem_2": "<p>1 fl oz — about a month of use</p>",
        "ggB9Gp8U8JQ_childItem_0": "<p>Why this isn’t like the other self-tanners</p>",
        "ggB9Gp8U8JQ_childItem_1": "<p>Will it turn me orange?</p>",
        "ggB9Gp8U8JQ_childItem_2": "<p>How long does it last?</p>",
        "ggB9Gp8U8JQ_childItem_3": "<p>How many drops?</p>",
        "ggB9Gp8U8JQ_childItem_4": "<p>How to use it</p>",
        "ggB9Gp8U8JQ_childItem_5": "<p>Good for sensitive skin?</p>",
        "ggB9Gp8U8JQ_childItem_6": "<p>Can I pay on delivery?</p>",
        "ggB9Gp8U8JQ_childItem_7": "<p>60-Day “Try It” Guarantee</p>",
        "ggCdVdus-lO_text": "<p>If it doesn’t live up to what we say, you’ve got 60 days to get every dollar back.<br>No hoops. No drama.</p>",
        "ggFipoBsWwP_text": "<p>Depends how dark you want to go.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Just a little color (barely there):</strong><br>3–4 drops<br>Once every 3–4 days</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Natural tan:</strong><br>5–6 drops<br>Twice a week</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Darker, more noticeable:</strong><br>7–8 drops<br>Three times a week</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Start light. You can always add more next time.</p>",
        "ggKZrkCgfQz_text": "<p>Most self-tanners are loaded with alcohol, fake fragrance, and just DHA.<br>That’s why they turn you orange and dry your face out.</p><p>SerlinoLab is different:</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>No alcohol.</strong> Easy on sensitive skin.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Double action: DHA + Erythrulose.</strong><br>DHA gives you color. Erythrulose makes it look like you actually got some sun — not like you lost a bet.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Italian carrot extract.</strong><br>Adds a warm, golden tone. Not pumpkin.</p><p><strong>Sodium Hyaluronate + Aloe Vera.</strong><br>Doesn’t just darken your skin. Helps with dry skin while it works.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Bottom line?</strong><br>A real tan. Healthier-looking skin. No clown face.</p>",
        "ggLuQ0nuQN8_text": "<p>No<br>The DHA + Erythrulose combo gives you a natural tone that looks like time outside — not a spray booth disaster.</p>",
        "ggNgskm7d42_text": "<p><strong>Step 1:</strong> Wash your face with the SerlinoLab cleanser. Clean skin = better, more even color.</p><p><strong>Step 2:</strong> Put the drops in your palm. Rub evenly over face and neck in circular motions.</p><p><strong>Step 3:</strong> Give it 15–20 minutes before you put on a shirt.</p><p>Wash your hands right after.</p><p>Pro tip: Exfoliate 24 hours before for the most even result.</p>",
        "ggR8kqovO2L_text": "<p>3–4 days.<br>Fades out evenly. No weird patches. No blotchy mess.</p>",
        "ggVLmbUDTCI_text": "<p><span style=\"font-size:23px;\">Self-Tanning Drops</span></p>",
        "ggWWrnyOmWZ_text": "<p>Yes.<br>Your order shows up in 24–48 hours.<br>Pay cash when it gets there.</p>",
        "ggbsEHDd1cH_label": "Add to Cart",
        "ggbsEHDd1cH_outOfStockLabel": "Out of stock",
        "ggbsEHDd1cH_unavailableLabel": "Unavailable",
        "ggbsEHDd1cH_variantSelectionRequiredMessage": "Please select a variant to add product to cart",
        "ggd3njxJyN7_text": "60-day Guarantee",
        "ggg59nFYXJE_text": "<p>Yes.<br>No alcohol.<br>Packed with Aloe Vera, Sodium Hyaluronate, and Vitamin E.</p><p>Works great even after shaving.</p>",
        "ggz0FAMQkBP_text": "<p>You’ve got 60 days to test it.<br>If you don’t like it, email us.<br>You get 100% of your money back.</p>",
        "section_preload": "true"
      },
