    "gp_section_608890156980109879": {
      "settings": {
        "checksum": "4cfe7be1897ac9cb18c2bf51b0076347137f29de97fa7a3ce8d9bf175fc5a195_1_1_1_0__1",
        "gg0zbjVVCnF_label": "<p>DHA + Erythrulose</p>",
        "gg1j4ei5grg_label": "<p><strong>Sodium Hyaluronate</strong></p>",
        "gg2yGs5LDlR_text": "<p><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;\">AQUA [WATER], GLYCERIN, ALOE BARBADENSIS LEAF JUICE (*), DIHYDROXYACETONE, ERYTHRULOSE, CARAMEL, PHENOXYETHANOL, POLYSORBATE 20, XANTHAN GUM, ZEA MAYS (CORN) GERM OIL, SODIUM HYALURONATE, TOCOPHERYL ACETATE, ETHYLHEXYLGLYCERIN, CITRIC ACID, PARFUM [FRAGRANCE], SODIUM BENZOATE, TETRAMETHYL ACETYLOCTAHYDRONAPHTHALENES, POTASSIUM SORBATE, DAUCUS CAROTA (CARROT) SATIVA ROOT EXTRACT</span></p>",
        "ggLeqJI7XQW_childItem_0": "<p>Full Ingredient List</p>",
        "ggU84KAzI43_text": "<p>This is the combo that matters.<br>DHA gives you color.<br>Erythrulose makes it even and natural.</p><p>Together, they stop that cheap self-tanner orange look.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Benefits:</strong><br>• Looks like a real sun tan<br>• Zero orange effect<br>• Even color, no patchiness</p>",
        "ggkvOXZntCM_text": "<p>Italian-sourced ingredients. No filler. No nonsense.</p>",
        "ggq2VeAT1Um_text": "<p>From farms in Abruzzo and Emilia Romagna. High in beta-carotene.<br>Gives you a warm, golden tone. Not orange.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Benefits:</strong><br>• Natural golden color<br>• Warm undertone<br>• Helps nourish skin while it works</p>",
        "ggtOVHAQdCx_text": "<p>Not just color. Helps with dry skin too.<br>Locks in moisture so your face feels smooth instead of tight.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Benefits:</strong><br>• Deep moisture<br>• Softer skin<br>• Better-looking tan</p>",
        "ggv1U-w8hnC_label": "<p>Italian Carrot Extract</p>",
        "ggwTMw9UkAs_text": "<span style=\"color:#17162E;\">What your skin actually needs. Nothing else.</span>"
      },
      "type": "gp-section-608890156980109879"
    },
