        "gg0JcSIpWVP_text": "<p>Made in our family lab on the Amalfi Coast.<br>We’ve been at this for over 30 years.</p><p>Italian-grown ingredients. Sourced from local farmers.<br>&nbsp;</p><p>Zero junk:<br>No silicones. No parabens. No alcohol. No synthetic fragrance. Cruelty-free.</p>",
