        "gg5r67GKkA8_childItem_4": "<p><span style=\"background-color:rgb(239,240,241);color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:16px;\">Is it good for sensitive skin?</span></p>",
        "gg5r67GKkA8_childItem_5": "<p><span style=\"background-color:rgb(239,240,241);color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:16px;\">Can I pay on delivery?</span></p>",
        "ggBr_m71saN_text": "<p>Depends how dark you want to go.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Light — just a touch of color</strong><br>3–4 drops<br>Once every 3–4 days</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Medium — natural tan</strong><br>5–6 drops<br>Twice a week</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Darker — more noticeable</strong><br>7–8 drops<br>Three times a week</p><p>Start on the lower end.</p><p><br>You can always go darker next time.</p>",
        "ggE2a9V-meS_text": "<p>3–4 days.<br>Even color.<br>Fades out slowly. No spots. No weird patches.</p>",
        "ggKeQeBypCw_text": "<p>Most self-tanners are packed with alcohol, fake fragrance, and just DHA.<br>That’s why they dry your face out and turn you orange.</p><p>SerlinoLab is built different:</p><p><strong>No alcohol.</strong> Easy on sensitive skin.</p><p><strong>DHA + Erythrulose.</strong><br>DHA gives you the color.<br>Erythrulose makes it look real. Like you got sun — not sprayed in a booth.</p><p><strong>Italian carrot extract.</strong><br>Adds a warm, golden tone. Not that fake pumpkin shade.</p><p><strong>Sodium Hyaluronate + Aloe Vera.</strong><br>It doesn’t just give you color. It helps with dry skin while it’s working.</p><p><strong>End result?</strong><br>Natural tan. Better-looking skin.</p>",
        "gg__kifShYw_text": "<span style=\"color:#17162E;\">Do You Still Have Any Doubts?</span>",
        "gglFYYGZwgb_text": "<p>Yes.</p><p>You’ll get your order in 24–48 hours.<br>Pay cash when it shows up.</p>",
        "ggzn9yZbmxc_text": "<p>Yes.</p><p>No alcohol.<br>Made with Aloe Vera, Sodium Hyaluronate, and Vitamin E to calm and support the skin.</p><p>Works great even after shaving.</p>"
