        "ggoN41NO0dB_text": "<p>“At my brother’s wedding people kept asking where I went on vacation. I was home the whole time.”</p>",
        "ggoZwto1HxO_text": "<p><strong>— Paul C.</strong>, 51, verified buyer</p>",
        "ggrQd1iPxbw_text": "<p>“Tried other self-tanners. All of them turned me orange or blotchy. This one doesn’t. Finally.”</p>",
        "ggtjvmHBq8W_text": "<p>“I hate sitting in the sun but I was pale as hell. Now I’ve got color year-round. Stupid easy to use.”</p>"
